OL,3,CWhere is the #470,000 fine Birmingham
OL,4,CCity Council has paid itself going?
OL,6,FBirmingham City Council has admitted
OL,7,Fthat 'many' of their more than 1000-
OL,8,Fstrong fleet of vehicles have not been
OL,9,Fcompliant with their own Clean Air
OL,10,FZone (CAZ), and therefore have been
OL,11,Fsubject to paying the daily fee.
OL,13,FThis has resulted in more than
OL,14,F#470,000 being paid to itself in
OL,15,Fcharges and fines because its own
OL,16,Fvehicles break the rules of the scheme
OL,17,Fwhich aims to tackle city centre
OL,18,Fpollution.
OL,20,FWhat will happen to the fines?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
