OL,3,CWhere is the #470,000 fine Birmingham
OL,4,CCity Council has paid itself going?
OL,6,FThe money will go towards the CAZ
OL,7,Foperating costs and covering some
OL,8,FGovernment charges.
OL,10,FThe council said "It is important to
OL,11,Fnote that any surplus has to be spent
OL,12,Fon transport or environmental schemes
OL,13,F- it cannot go back into the council's
OL,14,Fgeneral funds."
OL,16,FHow did this happen?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
